      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WIN'S FOR FUN (2) is better than last start when sixth (23.51) in a Grade 5/6 at this track over 400m. Has a good record at this journey. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. SON OF ZATARA (1) goes very well this trip starting nine times for three wins and five minors. In the money last time at this track (17.38) in a Grade 5, finishing a 2 length second. Can feature in the finish. SALUTING CRAIG (8) goes very well this course and distance starting seven times for three wins and two minors. Missed the frame latest (18.24) when eighth over 297m at Northam in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and can measure up. LARA MAGIC (7) jumps at a shorter distance and still warrants respect.",
